    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into the exciting world of Proportions, a multiplayer game where players have different roles. Some players are Minis who need to complete tasks, while one player is the Giant trying to find and stop them. Use voice chat to talk to your team, but be careful—the Giant can hear you if you’re close!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><strong>Play as a Mini !</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/934f28de9482053a64433019afac0115.poster.avif?t=1750841178\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/934f28de9482053a64433019afac0115.webm?t=1750841178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/934f28de9482053a64433019afac0115.mp4?t=1750841178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete the objectives to defeat the giant.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/247f7e90d31ad448d3443fe6e206dfea.poster.avif?t=1750841178\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/247f7e90d31ad448d3443fe6e206dfea.webm?t=1750841178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/247f7e90d31ad448d3443fe6e206dfea.mp4?t=1750841178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bite the Giant to free yourself !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/bf7420c0d3741b41052a89cd8786a153.poster.avif?t=1750841178\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/bf7420c0d3741b41052a89cd8786a153.webm?t=1750841178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/bf7420c0d3741b41052a89cd8786a153.mp4?t=1750841178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free others from giant's traps !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/79d2665e6d7cf9ec2a493d244f641c68.poster.avif?t=1750841178\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/79d2665e6d7cf9ec2a493d244f641c68.webm?t=1750841178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/79d2665e6d7cf9ec2a493d244f641c68.mp4?t=1750841178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >…or end up in its traps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play as a Giant !</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/3c36bfb8102b20398035b241b8c58344.poster.avif?t=1750841178\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/3c36bfb8102b20398035b241b8c58344.webm?t=1750841178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/3c36bfb8102b20398035b241b8c58344.mp4?t=1750841178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Catch the Minis !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/6effb7e892b04d9aed15723b69e6f63f.poster.avif?t=1750841178\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/6effb7e892b04d9aed15723b69e6f63f.webm?t=1750841178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146590/extras/6effb7e892b04d9aed15723b69e6f63f.mp4?t=1750841178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>And trap them !</p>",
